Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标归根结底是永恒号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克·玖尔 决斗出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出击后射出救生舱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士靠近 对照热纹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ginn12 决斗 CGUE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色22.18D
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮瞄准 各舰集火永恒号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级接近 距离30
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色14.33-87C
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 克鲁泽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会挑时间挑地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔菲鲁特舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒号和草雉迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号对付主天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转向 黄色17.25A
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推进力70%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈特弗里德1号2号瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 扎夫特舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-1队去迎击Ginn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被骗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难说到底是谁被骗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级发射救生艇一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单方面告知后 就扔在这片宇域？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葫芦里卖得什么药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我们击毁它？回收它？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱的话未免太做作了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说 舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避 左转舵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面坐的 真的是俘虏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱成一锅粥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠M-1没法抗衡Ginn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被压制的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该去死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ginn算什么 Ginn算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就尽情地杀戮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足你们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号 大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔菲鲁特舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和草雉号一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中所有火力攻击梅萨琉斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破那艘船离开宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝那里冲过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会暴露在三艘船的交叉火力下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦突破 被追击的可能性也最低
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破梅萨琉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样下去被前后夹击也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成功便成仁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号自己能摆脱主天使号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有试试了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉基拉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号 是我 我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是芙蕾 芙蕾·阿尔斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自扎夫特救生艇的国际救难频道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什么这么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虏就是这女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个孩子吧 阿尔斯塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾祸 萨布纳克少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是已故外务次官乔治·阿尔斯塔的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 萨布纳克少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 但这不代表不是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束战争的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…她这话说得有点意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟带着什么呢 钥匙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西 您反而相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人都会感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听人说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束战争的钥匙云云
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破 拉米亚斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主天使号会保护她的 玛硫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:09:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状态 你打算一个人突击敌舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我伤害的她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有责任保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法抑制等离子残渣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护 柏瑞安开火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方也撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残存部队到坐标D0集结
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里和地球军交战毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 钥匙是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的带着？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着挺像那么回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁给你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克…克鲁泽队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴面具的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴…巴基露露中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 芙蕾·阿尔斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（反中子干扰系统）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经突触快烧断了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更换储热剂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家应该都很累
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说基拉晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该没有在战斗中受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难为他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傲慢 蛮横 还疑心病重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是孩子的时候他就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这种印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这种事…你信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是唯一一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有资格制裁全人类的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是劣质品？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基因序列短 老化快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错 穆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他眼里 没有过去也没未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定连自我也没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的大门即将打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这个世界也将结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个被欲望填满的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 要世界陪葬？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让他得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等他一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前大天使号上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基拉他们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定 不再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭吧 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人才会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉的梦 总是那么悲伤　　　{\alpha&HFF&}伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你存在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像都在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫薇拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲叫尤伦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤伦·响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…到底算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是根本 不应该出生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 妈妈说过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也是世界的　　　{\alpha&HFF&}的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要出生在 这个世界上　　　　　{\alpha&HFF&}上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你 我找到了幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想你 在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.41,0:23:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可持有 不可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它虽有禁忌的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却现实存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人将其封印
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦是人将其放出牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的光芒在夜空中散去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「噩梦重现」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击溃这闪耀的黑暗 高达

